snippet.title: Keylocker | Turn Based Cyberpunk Action  -  Classes Reveal Trailer 4K
snippet.description: Keylocker | Turn Based Cyberpunk Action, the rhythm JRPG about a world without music gets its first trailer showing the gameplay of its first 4 classes. The game will have branching classes from the first 4, different headgears per class and unique Skill Trees as well for each class. Meet Sequencer, Hacker, Juggernaut and Samurai!
